## Step 4: Create Documentation Site

### 4.1 Setup Docs App

```bash
# Using Astro for docs (fast, great DX)
cd apps
pnpm create astro@latest docs -- --template minimal --typescript strict
cd docs
pnpm add @astrojs/react @astrojs/tailwind tailwindcss
pnpm add -D @types/react @types/react-dom
```

### 4.2 Configure Astro

```javascript
// apps/docs/astro.config.mjs

import { defineConfig } from 'astro/config';
import react from '@astrojs/react';
import tailwind from '@astrojs/tailwind';

export default defineConfig({
  integrations: [
    react(),
    tailwind(),
  ],
  output: 'static',
});
```

### 4.3 Tailwind Config for Docs

```javascript
// apps/docs/tailwind.config.js

/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
module.exports = {
  darkMode: 'class',
  content: ['./src/**/*.{astro,html,js,jsx,md,mdx,ts,tsx}'],
  theme: {
    extend: {
      // Glass effect utilities
      backdropBlur: {
        glass: '16px',
      },
      // Custom colors
      colors: {
        background: 'hsl(var(--background))',
        foreground: 'hsl(var(--foreground))',
      },
      // Custom animations
      animation: {
        'shine': 'shine 1.5s ease-in-out infinite',
        'float': 'float 3s ease-in-out infinite',
      },
      keyframes: {
        shine: {
          '0%': { transform: 'translateX(-100%)' },
          '100%': { transform: 'translateX(100%)' },
        },
        float: {
          '0%, 100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)' },
          '50%': { transform: 'translateY(-10px)' },
        },
      },
    },
  },
  plugins: [
    require('tailwindcss-animate'),
  ],
};
```

---

## Step 5: Install Dependencies

```bash
# Return to root
cd ../..

# Install all dependencies
pnpm install

# Build core package first
pnpm --filter @zenui/core build

# Build React package
pnpm --filter @zenui/react build

# Start docs development
pnpm --filter docs dev
```

---

## Step 6: Create Your First Page

### 6.1 Docs Layout

```astro
---
// apps/docs/src/layouts/Layout.astro
interface Props {
  title: string;
}

const { title } = Astro.props;
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <title>{title} | ZenUI</title>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-slate-950">
  <slot />
</body>
</html>
```

### 6.2 Component Demo Page

```astro
---
// apps/docs/src/pages/components/glassmorphic/glass-card.astro
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { GlassCardDemo } from '../../../components/demos/GlassCardDemo';
---

<Layout title="Glass Card">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Glass Card</h1>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-8">
      A beautiful frosted glass card with backdrop blur effect.
    </p>
    
    <!-- Live Preview -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
      <GlassCardDemo client:load />
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
```

---

## Step 7: Test Your Component

```bash
# Run docs dev server
pnpm --filter docs dev

# Open http://localhost:4321/components/glassmorphic/glass-card
```

---

## Common Commands Reference

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `pnpm install` | Install all dependencies |
| `pnpm dev` | Start all dev servers |
| `pnpm build` | Build all packages |
| `pnpm --filter @zenui/core build` | Build only core |
| `pnpm --filter @zenui/react build` | Build only React |
| `pnpm --filter docs dev` | Start docs dev server |
| `pnpm add <pkg> --filter <workspace>` | Add dep to specific package |

---

## Troubleshooting

### Issue: Module not found
```bash
# Rebuild all packages
pnpm build
```

### Issue: TypeScript errors
```bash
# Check TypeScript
pnpm tsc --noEmit
```

### Issue: Tailwind not working
- Ensure `tailwind.config.js` content paths are correct
- Restart dev server after config changes

